C%A5\" title=\"Reconstruction:Proto-Indo-European/wÃ³drÌ¥\">*wÃ³drÌ¥</a></i> <span class=\"mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren\">(</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-double-quote\">â€œ</span><span class=\"mention-gloss\">water</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-double-quote\">â€</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren\">)</span>.\n</p>\n<div class=\"NavFrame\">\n<div class=\"NavHead\" style=\"text-align: left;\">cognates</div>\n<div class=\"NavContent derivedterms\" style=\"text-align: left; column-count: 2; -moz-column-count: 2; -ms-column-count: 2; -o-column-count: 2; -webkit-column-count: 2;\">\n<p>Cognate with <span class=\"etyl\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scots_language\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Scots language\">Scots</a></span> <i class=\"Latn mention\" lang=\"sco\"><a href=\"/wiki/watter#Scots\" title=\"watter\">watter</a></i> <span class=\"mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren\">(</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-double-quote\">â€œ</span><span class=\"mention-gloss\">water</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-double-quote\">â€</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren\">)</span>, <span class=\"etyl\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saterland_Frisian_language\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Saterland Frisian language\">Saterland Frisian</a></span> <i class=\"Latn mention\" lang=\"stq\"><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=woaterje&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"woaterje (page does not exist)\">woaterje</a></i> <span class=\"mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren\">(</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-double-quote\">â€œ</span><span class=\"mention-gloss\">to water</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-double-quote\">â€</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren\">)</span>, <span class=\"etyl\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/West_Frisian_language\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:West Frisian language\">West Frisian</a></span> <i class=\"Latn mention\" lang=\"fy\"><a href=\"/w/index.php?ti